{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tutorial-js","path":"/zh/tutorial/Visualization/BrowseMap/Scrolling/","webpackCompilationHash":"b56fc1f276773fcd7503","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>当用户在地图窗口中操作时，如果想平移地图以便查看没有显示在地图窗口中地图部分，并且不方便切换地图窗口中的操作状态为漫游地图状态，可开启自动滚屏功能。</p>\n<h3 id=\"操作步骤\"><a href=\"#%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><img src=\"/read-56e09d9020b6fe36d2da63ae2fd275c5.gif\">操作步骤</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>在“ <strong>地图</strong> ”选项卡中“ <strong>浏览</strong> ”组中，单击“ <strong>设置</strong> ”下拉按钮，在下拉菜单中选中“ <strong>自动滚屏</strong> ”即可。</li>\n<li>在弹出的“设置”对话框中勾选“ <strong>自动滚屏</strong> ”复选框，实现自动滚屏，即当鼠标靠近地图窗口的边界时（如下面左图所示），鼠标自动变化为自动滚屏的状态，此时，单击鼠标左键，将实现地图的一次平移（如下面右图所示）。      </li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dc84afcd781cdeae9fd92af135f42c71/0c722/scrollscreen.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 322px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 78.26086956521739%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"scrollscreen\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/dc84afcd781cdeae9fd92af135f42c71/0c722/scrollscreen.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dc84afcd781cdeae9fd92af135f42c71/6a467/scrollscreen.png 210w,\n/static/dc84afcd781cdeae9fd92af135f42c71/0c722/scrollscreen.png 322w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 322px) 100vw, 322px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </th>\n<th>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/61f1b040c08e69c1a84474a94966cb35/0c722/scrollscreen2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 322px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 78.26086956521739%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"scrollscreen2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/61f1b040c08e69c1a84474a94966cb35/0c722/scrollscreen2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/61f1b040c08e69c1a84474a94966cb35/6a467/scrollscreen2.png 210w,\n/static/61f1b040c08e69c1a84474a94966cb35/0c722/scrollscreen2.png 322w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 322px) 100vw, 322px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>图：自动滚屏前</td>\n<td>图：自动滚屏后</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>当地图窗口中的操作状态为“放大”、“缩小”、“自由缩放”、“漫游”时，自动滚屏功能不可用。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"启用自动滚屏","next":null,"prev":null},"fields":{"path":"content\\tutorial\\Visualization\\BrowseMap\\Scro